description: PROPERTY WAS PREVIOUSLY A 12 BED ADULT LIVING FACILITY. CAN BE RETURNED TO A FOURPLEX AND OR POSSIBLE USAGE AS CHILD CARE AND OR RE-HAB,

Great property in Hialeah, FL; centrally located in Miami-Dade County!!! Recently renovated including tile, new central A/C, roof and Hurricane Impact windows. Includes split floor plan with master suite in the rear, which can easily be converted into in-law quarters with private entrance. Circular driveway and finished parking for a boat or RV. Big shed and above ground pool. 6 ft. metal privacy fence. Close to schools, shopping, dining/entertainment and close to all major highways. Your family and friends will also enjoy an 660 sq. ft. insulated covered patio perfect for family gatherings.

GREAT LOCATION! Centralized in Hialeah, this beautiful homes offers 4 bedrooms 2 bathrooms. Newly renovated Kitchen with all new Stainless steel appliances, this open concept kitchen elongates the family room, kitchen and dinning area. Large master bedroom with its on-suite master bathroom. Great size yard ready for entertaining. Investors property primary zoning is 4600 MULTI-FAMILY - 5 STORY

Impeccably maintained Four-Plex Newly built in 2006 solid CBS with new building codes. No capital expenditures needed ready to close and start collecting. Great Hialeah location, close to the airport, US27, Major Hwys, Shopping and Hialeah downtown business district.Units equipped with brand new Kitchen Cabinets and Granite Countertop/Stainless Steel Appliances/Bldg Security Cameras /Brand new white Zebra Blinds on all windows/ Full pest control treatment/Substantial upkeep and upgrades. No deferred maintenance. All legal construction. New tenants. Sale Not Subject to Appraisal.

Beautiful and very spacious 4/2 property with pool. Brand new kitchen with all new stainless steel appliances. Space on the sides plus a huge driveway and backyard as well. Bedroom windows are impact windows. A/C is just a couple years old and the roof is in perfect conditions. FULLY REMODELED AND BRAND NEW APPLIANCES!!

LOCATION!! LOCATION!! beautiful renovated home in the heart of Hialeah. this 4/2 property has a spacious backyard to accommodate future expansion for a growing family. Larger than tax roll. actual sq ft 2340 Must wear mask when showing Ty

Move in Ready, 3 bedrooms and 1 bath home will captivate you with its open porch. It has new laminate flooring throughout whole house, central a/c, updated kitchen and bathroom, iron bar protection and a large terrace. Large shed and fruit trees in the back yard.
Great Corner home with pool, a privacy wall and new Roof. You cant go wrong with this opportunity to enjoy your time off relaxing in your back patio nd pool in complete privacy.This will not last.

EXCELLENT TRIPLEX LOCATED IN COMMERCIAL ZONE. GREA FOR COMMERCIAL, RESIDENTIAL AND OFFICE. GREAT PROPERTY IN A CORNER LOT (APROX 10, 000 SQFT). TOTALLY UPGRADED 3 UNITS WITH CENTRAL A/C, SEPARATE METERS (1 SUBMETER) TENANTS PAY ALL UTILITIES, VERY GOOD FOR INVESTORS!!!

Great home investment opportunity in South-East Hialeah. House will be completely remodeled, prior to sale. Currently, there is a Tennant at the premises. Property offers many possibilities! Currently, four bedroom, two full bath, and one half a bath. Great income potential, as can be divided into a duplex.

This unapproved Duplex is located in East Hialeah, steps from the upcoming area of Leah of the Arts and close to public transportation, minutes from 826, Okeechobee Rd and Miami International Airport. This home was originally a 2 bedroom, 1 bath home and converted into a Duplex. Front unit is a 2 bedroom/ 1 bath (leased $1300 per month), Back unit is a 1 bedroom/ 1 bath (leased $850 per month). This property sits on a large 10k+ lot with potential. Owner started the process for rezoning to a duplex but was never completed which new buyer can continue the process and renovated to increase cashflow. Great property for an investor. Please do not approach tenants. Appointment required to show property 24 hours prior.

Great opportunity to purchase this 6 bedroom 6 bath home in a great location close to the airport, public transportation, downtown and expressways. The home sits on two lots. All windows except the back-sliding glass door are hurricane impact windows. Updated kitchen and bathroom tiled throughout. The house has electric front gates and Alexa controls the thermostat, doors, ADT alarm, and lights. The home has two tankless water heaters. Enjoy your backyard oasis with a pool and ample room to entertain.

LARGE 5/3 in the heart of Hialeah with a HUGE LOT AND BACKYARD. CENTRALLY LOCATED IN THE MOST IDEAL AREA OF HIALEAH. WILLING TO HEAR AND LISTEN TO OFFERS. Needs some TLC, currently rented for $3, 200. Property can be yours or for INVESTORS and NEW BUYERS! TENANTS CAN STAY OR GO BEFORE CLOSING. Tenants needs 60 days for closing.

Excellent Property for development 10, 105sf, mainly for a clinic, town houses, offices and more. One minute from the train station of Hialeah. Property is centered in downtown Hialeah. Primarily zoned for Commercial - Neighborhood.

This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home with utility shed and covered parking. Gas stove, newer central A/C and appliances, concrete roof and newer tile are some of the improvements to this fenced in home. Sold As-Is. Shed in backyard NOT included in sale of home.
$$$ TURNKEY DUPLEX $$$ EASY TO RUN ! Perfectly located Duplex with TWO - 2 beds / 1 full baths .Please ! Refer to Brokers Remarks. Pls. Do not Disturb tenants.
Location, Location, Location. 2 bedroom 1 & 1/2 bath townhouse condo. There is a nice patio in the rear and 2 parking spaces directly in front of the unit. Walk to shopping and public transportation.

Excellent home with a big Florida room, great rental potential to easy add 2 efficiencies or one bedroom and one efficiency. Located in a cul de sac (very quiet residential street). Nice size lot with a shed and a potential to have a pool. New A/C unit. Much more. Wont last. Easy to show.
THE PERFECT HOUSE TO ENJOY WITH THE FAMILY !!!!, CALL ME NOW !!!!!

SPACIOUS 2 BEDROOMS 2 FULL BATHS , ON THE FIRST FLOOR , TILES FLOORS THROUGH OUT HOME .CENTRALLY LOCATED IN THE HEART OF HIALEAH. NEW A/C UNIT . HANDICAP ACCESSIBLES . LOW MAINTANCE FEE , PARKING AREA QUITE COMPLEX .
THIS UNIT IS READY TO MOVE IN All RENOVATED UNIT 3 BEDROOM AND 2 FULL BATH RENOVATED PATIO STAINLESS STEEEL APPLIANCES EASY TO SHOW AND READY TO SELL MUST SEE FOR SHOWING CALL LISTING AGENT.
Hialeah remodeled home! This home features a spacious living room, dining room, remodeled kitchen 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, family, large backyard. Much more! Wont last!

1772 sf building with slight fire damage in 1/7th of it. Marked as unsafe structure by a violation issued by the City of Hialeah after incident. Building is to be completely remodeled/redone OR bulldozed to re-built. If you are a builder/general contractor: THIS IS YOUR OPPORTUNITY. Current land use is R1 (Single home), could easily turn into R2 to build a new duplex Possible Rendering attached on pictures), and Zoning is 4600/MULTY-FAMILY-5 STORY AND UP.. Just at one block from Palm ave, in the heart of downtown Hialeah, close to shopping, restaurants, city hall, and all new developments. Cash or hard money only, due to conditions. Do your due diligence before placing an offer. PLEASE, READ THIS MLS & TAX REPORT BEFORE CALLING.COME SEE IT. NO WHOLESELLERS, PLEASE.

Estate Sale, all offers are subject to Probate Court Approval. Spacious home with great potential to be made into a Duplex legally. Needs complete rehab and will need to comply with City of Hialeah required corrections. Centrally located close to schools, shopping, public transportation, major highways and Miami International airport. Being sold AS IS. See Broker Remarks

description: Stunning and move in ready 5 bedroom, 3 baths home in the exclusive, gated community of Miami Lakes Loch-Lomond. FULLY UPGRADED home with the finest finishes, spectacular chef kitchen with top of the line stainless steel appliances (Wolf, Sub-Zero & Miele) overlooking the pool area. Elegant and spacious master-bedroom, large master bath with double shower under a beautiful natural skylight and built-in walking closet with ample space. Marble floors all throughout and wood floors in bedrooms. Fenced backyard with heated pool, spa and built-in BBQ grill. Plenty of parking space area with carport and 2 car garage. Impact windows and doors. This is the perfect home for a family and guests.

Courtyard villa bright open floor plan, private courtyard high ceilings spacious master Bdrm, two upstairs loft area to use as an office /den/bedroom. walking distance to Miami lakes main street shops, restaurants and parks. Low Assoc Dues $850/yr . DO NOT DISTURB TENANTS.

ELEGANT AND SPACIOUS 5 BEDROOM, 3 FULL BATH HOME, SITTING ON A SERENE LAKE. HOME HAS TILE FL0ORS THROUGHOUT, SPACIOUS AND BRIGHT BEDROOMS, LARGE KITCHEN WITH PLENTY OF STORAGE, IMPACT WINDOWS AND DOORS THROUGHOUT, NEW HIGH EFFICIENCY A/C. HOME HAS AN ENCLOSED TERRACE THAT IS PERFECT FOR ENJOYING THE VIEW, OR ENJOYING A NICE MEAL WITH FAMILY. A+ SCHOOLS IN AREA. NATURAL GAS AVAILABLE. NEAR SHOPPING AND MAJOR HIGHWAYS. NO ASSOCIATION. LOOK NO FURTHER, THIS HOME IS ONE OF A KIND.

Beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath in the center of Hialeah with impact windows and in great condition! All bathrooms remodeled; brand new a/c unit; ceramic flooring throughout; parking big enough for 4 vehicles; no HOA. Great location in close proximity to malls, restaurants, schools and parks. Only 15 minutes to Miami International Airport. Owner occupied. Showings will be any time after 4pm during the week and anytime on the weekend. 24 hour notice required to show.
Nice 1/1 condo in West Hialeah, with stainless steel appliances. 24 hrs notice for all showings.

Location location location. This ideal home sits on a great sized lot Located on the incredible oak lined Aberdeen way in the security guard house gated prestigious community of Loch Lomond. Working fireplace and well laid out with plenty of room for entertain indoors and out with a covered terrace that faces the oversized pool. Dont miss this one!!
Great Location ! Well Maintained Villa/Tonwhouse . close to major highway, school and stores. Newly painted outside.

Excellent opportunity to own a corner unit Townhouse with view to the lake, with access and view from the master bedroom, in Miami Lakes area. Great outdoor area to entertain family and guests. The awning was recently replaced. Corner unit has 3 available parking space. Major Highway is less than 5 miles away, plenty of great restaurants in the area. Open kitchen layout with view to the terrace and the lake. 3 bedroom and 2 baths, Master bedroom is towards the back for great privacy. Easy to see and ready for the new owners to enjoy!

RARE CYPRESS VILLAGE SPACIOUS 3 Bedroom 2 Bath unit situated in the heart of Miami Lakes. Stainless steel appliances, washer and dryer inside unit. Conveniently located near Cypress Village Shopping Center, Main Street, restaurants and the Palmetto Expressway.

Come see this cozy 2/2 condo in the beautiful Miami lakes! With a recently remodeled bathroom, first floor unit for comfort and spacious patio, great for BBQ! There is nothing more you could ask for in a condo. Walking distance from shops and restaurants, great schools and parks. I guarantee your client will love this place! Bring them asap. The unit is vacant!

Corner unit on the 2nd floor right across from clubhouse and Pool in Cypress village in the heart of Miami Lakes . Great for investment or as a starter home. Amenities include 2 pools and tennis courts. Night security guard. Walking distance to shops and main street . Minutes away from 826/I75. Accordion shutters .condo qualifies for 3% down payment financing

Beautiful, cozy, clean, secure, spacious are just a few of the words that come to mind when describing this property. This 3 bedroom two and half bathroom has so much to offer. Large Laundry room and bonus room are located downstairs to accommodate someone that has difficulties climbing stairs. Large bedrooms with bathroom in each bedroom upstairs. Cozy back area for afternoon BBQ. All windows are hurricane secure ready for Florida storms. No association! No association! Text agent for showing appointment

Rare opportunity to live on the biggest lot Miami Lakes has to offer. Located inside the guard-gated & golf course community of Loch Lomond, this home sits on 1.92 acres, occupying the largest lakefront property in the area. This custom estate boasts just under 8,000 sqft of complete privacy. This palatial home displays a resort-style pool area, beach entrance, numerous docks, plus a large outdoor pavilion complete with a built-in BBQ area. The home shows a grand master suite and has over 275 feet of direct lakefront access, providing unrivaled lakefront views throughout. This listing includes a separate 20,909 sqft lake-front lot with separate folio (#32-20-14-006-0020) valued at over $650,000.

Check out this 4 beds/3 baths single family home, nestled in a desirable Hialeah area. Very well maintained home as pride is in the ownership. House also features in-law quarters. Schedule your showing today.

Spacious and very well maintained two story 3/2.5 Townhome at Palm Spring Villas. It offers tiles throughout, stainless steel appliances. granite counter tops, large and spacious living room and kitchen areas. Property has accordion shutters and lots of storage space. Very low maintenance fee This unit has a large backyard that faces Amelia Earhart park . Easy to show . Call listing agent.

LOCATION LOCATION, ONE IN A MILLION OPORTUNITY IN A RESIDENTIAL AREA IN HIALEAH, ONE CAR GARAGE, EXTENDED PATIO, COVERED SIDE ENTRANCE, FENCED IN PATIO, ALL OFFERS MUST BE PRESENTED IN A FARBAR ASIS CONTRACT WITH PROOF OF FUDNS AND ESCROW DEPOSIT CHECK, All offers must be submitted by the buyers agent using the online offer management system. Access the system via the link below. A technology fee will apply to the buyers agent upon consummation of a sale Buyers highest and best offer has been requested

Beautiful property in the desired area of west Hialeah and Miami Lakes, easy access to Palmetto expressway, Markets, A+ schools and much more. Pool view, best located unit in the complex.Hurry, it wont last!

Own this wonderfully maintained, one-story single-family home featuring 3 bedrooms & 2 baths in West Hialeah. This house has a fantastic layout with a living room, dining room, family room, laundry room with storage space off the kitchen, and a covered terrace. Plus a bonus bedroom that was added with permits, right off the kitchen, and a covered terrace. Plus a bonus bedroom that was added with permits, right off the covered terrace. This bonus room was used as a mans cave by the previous owner and can be used as a 4th bedroom. The home is tiled throughout, has a large storage shed in the ample backyard, an outside utility room with a generator, and a circular driveway. Centrally located near Miami Lakes, shopping centers, restaurants, schools & more.

Very Well kept Larger Townhome 3/3 Full Baths Must see to appreciate, Larger model than others in this T/House Community (AS PER OWNER 1800 Sq.Ft. Florida Room) Florida/Office/Den Room is Currently split in half, Parking for up to 4 cars, Large Master Bedroom w/walk-in closet, 1st Floor has full bath, Master Bath Spa Tub, Separate Large Wash/Dryer Room, 3.5-ton RHEEM AC (2016), Kitchen Cabinets and Island (2017) ROOF (Main and Fl. Room) & Gutters (2019) WITH PERMITS Wind Mitigation has been updated for less insurance premiums Exterior Paint (2019) Hurricane HVHZ Windows 1st Floor (2020) Accordion Shutters 2nd Floor (2020) As per the owner, the property is bigger is larger than the tax roll 50 Yards to the private community walk-in entrance to Amelia Earhart Park HOA ($19.00 per month)

Nice house on one of the best Hialeah West neighborhood , new impact windows , new pavers circular drive way , new roof , not neighbors on back , very closed to express ways , you can have a Four bedroom if needed or in law quarter , fruit trees , new metal fence on part of house

BACK ON THE MARKET! QUIET FAMILY COMMUNITY AND WITHOUT HOA!!! THIS HOME IS MINUTES FROM RESTAURANTS, SHOPPING, HOSPITALS, A-RATED SCHOOLS AND MAJOR HIGHWAYS. THE HOME FEATURES 2 MASTER BEDROOMS WITH PRIVATE BATHROOMS, A THIRD LIVING AREA THAT CAN BE CONVERTED INTO A BEDROOM, COVERED PATIO FOR ENTERTAINMENT WITH A STORAGE SHED, LARGE CARPORT AND RECENTLY RENOVATED KITCHEN AND BATHROOMS WITH NEW APPLIANCES. PROPERTY IS TENANT OCCUPIED UNTIL MAY 1ST, 2021 AND ALL SHOWINGS ARE BY APPOINTMENT ONLY.
INVESTORS DREAM, NO RENTAL RESTRICTION. HUGE APARTMENT 1316 SF, CORNER UNIT, 3 BEDROOMS, 2 BATHROOMS. OPEN BALCONY, SECURE BUILDING, ELEVATOR, GREAT LOCATION, COMMUNITY POOL. JUST FULL OFFERS.

One of a kind townhouse for sale, this is one in a life time opportunity to own this completely remodeled townhome in the best area of Hialeah. To Begin with, there is one room that can easily be converted to a bedroom in the first floor, the townhouse features TWO AC units, one in the first floor and one in the second floor, remodeled granite kitchen, remodeled half bathroom downstairs, marble stairs, remodeled marble master bathroom featuring a state of the art jacuzzi and shower and marble vanity top, custom built closet, remodeled bathroom in the second bedroom, hurricane impact sliding door and window and so much more. ONLY $19.00 HOA. Centrally located just minutes away from taking State Road 924 which connects Interstate 75 and the Palmetto Expressway North or South.
No Association! Beautiful townhouse 3 bedrooms 2 and half bathrooms in the heart of Hialeah.

Spacious 2 bedroom 2 1/2 Bathroom with Lakeview. Bonus room on 1st floor which could be used as 3rd bedroom or office. Brand new roof installed 2018 and brand new A/C unit installed 2019. Huge courtyard in the front for entertaining or you can take your guest to the back yard to enjoy the Lakeview on the deck. Endless possibilities with this townhome.

Beautiful fully remodeled townhouse all new windows and doors with anti-hurricane panels in the center of town in a very desirable neighborhood close to good schools, parks, shopping malls, and main highways easy to show with 24 hour notice, call listing agent please. Very low maintance New high-efficiency A/C unit. Tiled floors, Do not miss this opportunity .

MOVE IN READY, 5/4 with an office. Great income potential in the heart of Hialeah. 2 Master Bedrooms. Newly remodeled pool with a slide. Pool bathroom. Accordion shutters throughout this home. Oasis backyard with beautiful and mature avocado and mango trees. Move into this quiet neighborhood with good schools and a backyard your family will love. Covered patio for family gatherings. Covered carport for your toys behind secure gates. Permanent Generac generator so you dont have to worry about power during/after hurricanes. Close to schools, church, shopping and major highways. This home will not last. Come see it today! Selling AS-IS

Hope you are packed up and ready to move because this beautiful house was made for you! Great 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in the city of Hialeah. This property offers a fantastic layout with a warm-welcoming living room, charming kitchen alongside the dining room, four very nice commodious bedrooms including the master suite and guest quarters. Awesome backyard with a pool, covered patio, amazing space to entertain, relax and enjoy the gorgeous South Florida weather! Located in a lovely, family-friendly neighborhood with everything you need at your convenience. Just minutes away you have multiple shopping centers where you will find Publix Supermarket, restaurants, shops, Walgreens, daycares and so much more! You do not want this opportunity to pass you by!

GREAT INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY IN THE HEART OF HIALEAH! VERY WELL MAINTAIN UNIT FEATURING 2 BDRMS, 2 BATHS with NEUTRAL TILE THROUGHT, NICE SIZE KITCHEN & GREAT CITY VIEWS! ENCLOSED BALCONY FOR EXTRA LIVING SPACE. PRIVATE FENCED PARKING LOT. CASH ONLY PURCHASE @ ASKING PRICE SELLER WILL PAY FOR SPECIAL ASSESSMENT OF $16, 575 AT CLOSING! Perfect for a first time home buyer or investor special. Spacious 2/2 in Hialeah. Located on the first floor. Small backyard. Community is gated and you can only enter & exit with a clicker. AC unit is fairly new. Property is being sold AS IS. Property needs some TLC, Property has some water damage, in its current condition it was renting out for $1, 320.00 Most units are rented at $1, 500.00 and up thats a 12% ROI. Please text LA for showings.

Beautiful move-in ready apartment, updated kitchen and appliances, centrally located in Hialeah, near malls and markets, less than 5 minutes to the express way. Located on the first floor. Motivated seller. 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, one of them recently updated.

A must see one of a kind contemporary masterpiece Adorned with modern finishes & stunning highlights; enjoy fine living in over an acre of land. Outfitted with a custom glass-dome pavilion as you enter the property, this home welcomes you to enjoy the sheen Miami sunshine. Over 7000 sqft of construction feature 5 beds, 6 baths, plus office, media room, bar, breakfast lounge, fireplace sitting room, sun parlor, and an expansive gourmet kitchen by Italkraft with Miele appliances. The exterior sports a custom 6-hole mini golf course, LED lighted hardcourt tennis/basketball court and 28, 000-gallon oversized Pool with alfresco outdoor vibes & luscious landscaping overlooking expansive views on Don Shulas famed golf course. 14 Car Motorcourt. This home is waiting for a sophisticated new owner.

description: Stunning and move in ready 5 bedroom, 3 baths home in the exclusive, gated community of Miami Lakes Loch-Lomond. FULLY UPGRADED home with the finest finishes, spectacular chef kitchen with top of the line stainless steel appliances (Wolf, Sub-Zero & Miele) overlooking the pool area. Elegant and spacious master-bedroom, large master bath with double shower under a beautiful natural skylight and built-in walking closet with ample space. Marble floors all throughout and wood floors in bedrooms. Fenced backyard with heated pool, spa and built-in BBQ grill. Plenty of parking space area with carport and 2 car garage. Impact windows and doors. This is the perfect home for a family and guests.

Remodeled! Buyers Dream, 3 Bedroom 2 1/2 Bath home with 3, 500 sf of living area under air. Bamboo flooring throughout the entire home. Kitchen has Silestone Counters and Stainless Viking Appliances. Master Bath has Silestone Counters and Wenge Cabinets. Porcelain Exterior Patio tiles. Surrounded by lush landscaping. impact windows. The property has a standby generator that powers the entire house.

Beautiful single-family home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on a corner lot. The home has an open floorplan and lots of natural light. Brand new HVAC system and newly painted driveway. Fha buyers will not be able to purchase the property due to 90-day seasoning. Showings will commence Friday 4/30/21 and will stop 05/05/21.

Lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom family home in Hialeah. Here you have a charming layout with a wonderful front porch, great living space, large kitchen with SS appliances, oversized family room in the rear, laundry room, spacious bedrooms, and ample storage space throughout. You also have workshop/office space and nice sized garage with ample room for additional storage. Go out the back door and you will be pleased to find an enchanting paved backyard with a whimsical garden around the perimeter and a delightful covered deck in the corner where you can enjoy a relaxing outdoor dinner under the stars! All this home needs is your personal touch to be the house of your dreams! Everything you need nearby including shopping centers, schools, major roads and highways for an easy commute!

New Construction 2011 directly on the Golf Course in Miami Lakes, most prestigious Gated Community of Loch Lomond. Amazing entertainment for a large family: Pool Deck w/ Summer Kitchen, Huge Covered patio, Room for RV on almost 20, 000 sq ft lot. All Impact windows & Doors, electric hurricane rolldown shutters for the terrace. Matte Porcelain Tile in living areas & Bedrooms, the floors are granite in the foyer, Security Cameras, Generator for the entire house and all of its appliances. 1st Floor: 4 beds 2.5 baths + Office (5th bed), living, dining, family rooms, open Kitchen with Thermador Appliances, wine fridge, pot filler at the stove, gas, New ACs 2018. Upstairs: Family room with wet bar & huge terrace, Master Suite with huge walk in closet, addition 2 beds & Bath. Crestron system.
Great starter home for young or older couple. Close to everything.
COZY CONDO IN THE HEART OF HIALEAH, CLOSE TO EVERYTHING YOU NEED GREAT SCHOOLS, INCLUDING MAGNET OPTION SCHOOLS, 2 BEDROOM 1 BATHROOM, VERY LITTLE RESTRICTIONS,

Beautiful Townhouse fully remodeled. NO HOA. Conveniently located, walk or drive to supermarkets, shops, and more. Stamps concrete driveway. Hurricane rated front door and bedroom window with security gate. Custom wood bedroom closets. Marble bathroom, tile w/frameless shower glass door. Rear patio french travertine w/and Alphonso mango tree and beautiful lake view.

Location, location!!! Beautiful and renovated house located in the best area of Miami Lakes! 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, screened pool covered enclosure, 2 car garage, covered back patio, private backyard with mature peaceful landscaping and canal view. Open concept kitchen with 8 feet island, living room decorated with a modern featured wall designed by an interior designer, Partial Shutters, automatic irrigation system, pool underwater light, walking distance to Main Street. Current Living Area Sqft 2, 231. NO HOA! Wont last long on the market!

Welcome home to affordable and charming living in Cypress Village nestled amidst tree-lined canopies and tropical landscapes in the quaint town of Miami Lakes! This first floor residence offers spacious bedrooms, a private fenced patio, assigned parking plus multiple swimming pools, tennis and nearby golf. Youll find yourself enjoying biking and walking to the best of amenities for dining, shopping and playing. The Main Street is a place in itself to enjoy daily and on weekends. All of this just minutes to major highways for an easy commute anywhere you need to travel or work!

Beautiful 1 bedroom 1 bathroom condominium unit for sale in the heart of Hialeah. This is a corner unit on ground floor and just meters away from the community pool area. Centrally located Hialeah lake front home, featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 bath, beautiful lake views, 1 car garage, circular driveway with 2 electric fence, great community with access to express ways, call for more information, it has a new roof installed recently.

Beautiful and spacious apartment right next to palmetto Expressway, conveniently located, walk or drive to supermarkets, shops and more. PERFECT LOCATION CLOSE TO TRANSPORTATION, CORNER UNIT 2 BEDROOMS, 2 BATHS AND 2 KITCHENS, PATIO, PARKING FOR 4 TO 6 VEHICLES , LOW MAINTANCE FEE. 2 ELECTRICITY METERS .

Celebration Point! First Floor, 2 bedroom/2 bath.  Foyer entrance, spacious and bright, flowing floor plan with 1090 sq/ft. of living space.  Master bedroom has large walk in closet and separate vanity area.  Stainless steel appliances in kitchen, screened patio with access to beautiful green/garden area.  Community offers impeccable maintenance with buildings recently painted, screened enclosures and roofs replaced, and resort style pool refurbished.  Jogging and bike trails along the lake, BBQ pavilions, pet friendly, lots of parking, 24 hour security, and on-site management.  A+ location, close proximity to schools, shopping, dining and entertainment, places of worship and easy highway access.  This is Home!!

Spacious 3 bedrooms 3 full bathrooms plus a den/office, spacious living area, home in the heart of west Hialeah, short distance to elementary, middle and high school, close to major expressways (826 Palmetto and Gratigny expressways). Fully remodeled kitchen, granite countertops with 42" white cabinets, fully remodeled master bathroom, all rooms are spacious, huge covered patio great for entertainment or storage. Large circular driveway good for 5 vehicles. Easy to show.

Location! Location! Location! 2 Bedrooms plus a den in the first floor, with 2 and 1/2 bathrooms townhome in the heard of Hialeah. CASH ONLY. Investors welcome. Excellent source of income. Call listing agent for more info.

Large two bedroom condo conveniently on the first floor with large screened patio. Clean and ready for its new owner.The community offers pool, lots of green space and parking is never an issue. come and see it today.

Lovely 2 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom townhome in the heart of Hialeah with gorgeous water views and no HOA! From the curb appeal of the charming porch on the exterior to the updated features on the interior, this home has so much potential. This home features an open floor plan, beautifully wooden cabinetry in the kitchen and beautifully updated bathrooms. Views of the pool and screened-in patio can be appreciated from almost every room in this home. On the exterior of the home you will find a spacious patio and gorgeous lake views making this home perfect for outdoor entertaining where you and your guests can enjoy a true Florida lifestyle. Best of all this property is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and more.

In the middle of Miami Dade County north of Miami international Air Port located in Hialeah this 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms boost 852 sq ft of living space. Very nice gated and quiet community near major highways, shopping malls, shopping plazas, restaurants, schools, parks, entertainment and Hialeah Park Racing & Casino to enjoy.

Hurry this is a gem!! Updated 2 stories townhome without association!! New flooring, freshly painted, kitchen and bathrooms updated, good size of bedrooms and a big patio for your entertaining. Easy to show it!

LOW HOA ONLY $19!!! Townhouse Fee Simple, FHA offers welcomed! Newer kitchen with an open layout leading to living room and dining area. Two master bedrooms! Beautiful move-in ready apartment, updated kitchen and appliances, centrally located in Hialeah, near malls and markets, less than 5 minutes to the express way. Located on the first floor. Motivated seller. 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, one of them recently updated.

AMAZING OPPORTUNITY TO OWN A FULLY REMODELED MOVE IN READY UNIT!! 2/2 Condo in west hialeah. Open family/living room, Kitchen has granite countertops and breakfast nook. Bathrooms are fully remodeled with tile flooring and neutral color palette throughout. Low maintenance fee, includes trash and water. Quiet building with assigned Parking space. Unit overlooks pool area. This is a true turn key ready.

Appliances less than 3 years old, a/c under 4 years, w/d less than 1 yr old, new ceramic tiled floors recently painted interior, the association placed a new roof and exterior painted all building less than 4 years ago. Located by the front entry to the community so very easy access. Open parking so no worries park where you find a spot. Roaming security patrol. Amazing

description: Community features a clubhouse and pool, which are walking distance from your home.covered terrace, Large 4 Brooms, . 2 1/5 Bathrooms , master bedroom have a sitting area that can be used as an office.

Great family home!!! 3 bedroom /2 bath, living area, formal dining room, family room and tile throughout . This property is sits in a lot over 9, 200 Sf with space to expand home or add a pool. Located in a quiet neighborhood with excellent school board district. Conveniently located near to shopping center, restaurant and major roads and transportation. Contact listing agent for showing instruction.

Remarkable single family home with beautiful in ground pool in Spanish Lakes area. This home consists of 4 bdrms 2 1/2 baths with upgraded kitchen, granite counter tops, and stainless steel appliances. Entry living has upgraded 20X20 tiles, over sized master bedroom with his and her closets. Come and enjoy this family oriented area great for raising kids. Please contact Listing Agent for showing instructions .

Freshly painted single family home. Great location close to shopping centers, major highways, and the site for the new mega mall on I-75 which will increase the prices in the near future. Fenced backyard with no backdoor neighbors, leaving you with a ton of privacy. Wall to wall sliding doors that bring in plenty of natural light. Very low HOA. The one car garage was converted into an office could be easily turn back into a garage. Kitchen was remodeled with granite counter tops and wood cabinets. (As Is Contracts Only)

Remarkable townhome great for families and entertainment; over 1853 square feet of living space. The garage is perfect for storage, home-gym or parking a car. Beautiful vaulted ceilings, allowing natural light to illuminate the very spacious living room, dining area and kitchen. Just off the kitchen is an atrium, perfect for growing your own herbs and vegetables. In the dining area is a fireplace which has been converted into a storage nuke. The large covered patio is perfect for gatherings. Under the staircase is an extra storage closet. Large master bedroom upstairs is equipped with a walk-in closet with access to the attic and large master bath. The other 2 rooms are spacious and have custom-made closets. The upstairs has a full bath and a closet in the hallway for more storage.

Beautifully remodeled home with over $190k in upgrades, new impact doors and windows, new A/C, NEW Flooring, kitchen, baths and more, located in a great community, dont miss out.MUST SEE TO APPRECIATE, Bring your most exclusive clients. Owner motivated. Call now, show today and close tomorrow, your clients will love you.... Property NOT subject to appraisal......

Beautiful and meticulously maintained 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home in the sought after gated community of The Moors. This home is ready to move in and offers spacious living/family room areas and large master bedroom and master bathroom. Relax and enjoy your morning coffee or afternoon cocktail in your expansive and covered patio with large yard. Enjoy the community pool, club house, tennis courts or out door grill for you family events. Located just outside Miami Lakes and near major expressways, this home has all you need. Hurry and schedule your private tour today before its gone!

Unit is in need of a full rehab! Large split level corner unit with lots of potential. Ideal for an investor looking to rent out or fix and flip. Only cash or conventional offers (Lender will require 20% down). Easy to show on lockbox.

Beautiful first floor condo in Country Club of Miami, Best conditions, 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, parking assigned, guest parking, centrally located by Flamingo and Miami Gardens dr. lovely building lots of charm, exterior brick. Kitchen and refrigerator appliances will be bought new.

2 beds, 1 bath, Totally remodeled, New kitchen / windows / water heater / AC / walls / outlets. First-floor condo in the heart of Miami Lakes, Branch Lake, Park, Centrally Located, near to shopping centers, HOA 350$ a month + $35 every 3 months master association

Unit is in short, average condition, inspections are welcome sold as is, very well located near shopping centers, malls, great schools, main highways and hospitals, final price subject to lender approval.

3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom Property needs some work but has lots of potential. This is a Shortsale, Final Sales Price and contract terms subject to 3rd party approval. Title and escrow to be selected by the seller. Please send Prequalification and Proof of funds prior to scheduling property showings.

SHORTSALE SUBJECT TO LENDER APPROVAL . THIS UNIT HAS A LOT OF POTENTIAL. PROPERTY NEEDS MAJOR REHAB. KITCHEN AND BATHROOMS NEED TO BE COMPLETELY REDONE. FLOOR IN SECOND ROOM IS MISSING. THE A/C AND WATER HEATER NEED TO BE REPLACED, ALSO THE MAJOR APPLIANCES.MUST CLOSE/ESCROW WITH SELLERS CHOICE. ALL OFFERS SUBJECT TO 3RD PARTY APPROVAL.

description: Completely remodeled, new roof, new bathrooms, new kitchen, impact sliding doors and windows, porcelain on the floor.

Beautiful one story single home in PSN neighborhood!! 2 bedthrooms and 1 bathroom, circular driverway and oversized side yard with room for boat or RV. Stainless steel appliances, granite counter kitchen. As per tax records house is 3/1, third room was convert into a leaving room and can be converted back easily to original bedroom. Fenced backyard with a beatifull covered terrase overlooking a pool and Jacuzzi great for family gatherings and entertaining, tile throughout.

Spectacular Lot and Block 2 bd/ 2.5 bth located in Tuscan Lake Village, Miami Lakes area! You Do Not need 20% down. This property is completely remodeled with an eat in kitchen and stainless steel appliances. A/C is brand new 2019! Gorgeous travertine tile covered terrace. There is plenty of storage and closets. Close to malls, restaurants, and highways. Easy to show! Show and SELL!

BEAUTIFULL UNIT AT HIALEAH MIAMI LAKES AREA, LARGE ONE BEDROOM ONE BATH , HUGE MASTER BEDROOM, HUGE WALKING CLOSET, IS LIKE A SECOND BEDROOM , LARGE BALCONY FACES THE POOL , SECURITY GUARD PRESENT24 HOUS, IMPACT WINDOWS ALL OVER THE UNIT , TOTALLY REMODOLED, NEW APPLICANCES , FRESLY PAINTED , READY TO MOVE IN .SHOWING BY APPOINTMENT, ONLY 24 HOURS IN ADVANCE

BEAUTIFULL CORNER POOL HOME!!PALM SPRING NORTH desirable, hard to find area, enough room for a boat with a front and backyard entrance. No HOA. New roof and water heater in 2019.Oversized Master bedroom with direct French door access to the beautiful pool offering the perfect outdoor entertaining and kitchen with upgraded appliances, granite counter tops. Easy access to major highways, and close to schools!. WONT LAST!!! HURRY!!!

Beautiful Remodeled House New Kitchen All New SS Appliances Quartz Counter Tops and Splash Remodeled Bathrooms New Impact Windows plus Accordion Shutters Hurricane Proof Garage Door Alarm System Titan Water Heater New Wood Fence Painted Inside & Out New Driveway All Tile Floor Low Maintenance Fee $80 a Month
NEW LAMINATED FLOORS AND BEAUTIFUL GRANITE COUNTERTOP. CLOSE TO SCHOOLS! LOCATED IN THE HEART OF MIAMI LAKES. EASY ACCESS TO HIGHWAYS.

Beautiful well kept home 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, big patio with a cover awning in the desirable gated community of Turtle Run low maintenance fee, tile through out. master bedroom with walk in closet, granite counter top and new stainless steel appliances, ceiling fans and fixtures included, accordion shutters, brand new wood fence, new A/C carrier unit. Turn-key ready to move. Cozy community, close to major highways, near main street in Miami Lakes.

Very well maintained and spacious 2 bedroom 2 bathroom corner villa. Featuring new stainless steel appliances , new kitchen cabinets, new AC, new water heater & fenced in patio. The community features tennis courts a large pool, walking and bike path, playground for the kids with low HOA payments. Located close to shops, several major highways and parks. This property is perfect for first time homebuyers or investors looking for rental income. Hurry this wont last.

NO SHOWINGS BEFORE 5:30! BEAUTIFUL CORNER, SPACIOUS, BRIGHT, LIGHT, VERY WELL MAINTAINED CONDO WITH A LARGE PATIO IN ONE OF THE BEST LOCATIONS IN MIAMI LAKES! THE PATIO IS BIG -YOU CAN HAVE YOUR OWN BBQS, ITS PERFECT FOR RELAXING AND ENTERTAINING. MODERN KITCHEN, S/S APPLIANCES, A/C HANDLER, WATER HEATER ALL FROM 2015. 2 CONTIGUOUS PARKING SPACES CLOSE TO YOUR FRONT DOOR AND YOU CAN WASH YOUR CAR RIGHT THERE. COMMUNITY POOL WITH GAZEBO. CONDO FEES ARE ONLY $200.00 PM! THIS IS A WELL RUN ASSOCIATION WITH GREAT FINANCIALS. ROOFS ARE BEING REPLACED WITHOUT THE NEED OF A SPECIAL ASSESSMENT! THE LOCATION IS AWESOME, SO CLOSE TO EVERYTHING. THIS APARTMENT IS ONE OF A KIND AND YOULL LOVE LIVING HERE! MUST HAVE A PREAPPROVAL LETTER TO SHOW, NO EXCEPTIONS. PLEASE SEE ATTACHMENTS FOR FINANCIALS!

Your search is over. Welcome Home Gated Community, community pool, beautiful lake surrounds the community, 2 parking spots in front of the property, accordion shutters, over sized patio completely fenced in for extra privacy. A/C 2015, low hoa fees. This is a must see property, hurry before its gone!!

BEAUTIFUL UPGRADED CONDO IN DESIRABLE AREA WITH A LESS THAN 5 MINUTES DRIVE TO GROCERY SHOPPING PLAZA, NEAR I-75 AND 826 EXPRESSWAYS. LOCATED ON THE GROUND LEVEL WHICH MAKES IT PERFECT FOR AVOIDING ELEVATORS AND STAIRS. ENJOY THE NATURAL LIGHT THAT COMES FROM CEILING TO FLOOR IMPACT WINDOWS IN EVERY ROOM OF THE UNIT. LARGE WALK-IN CLOSETS IN BOTH ROOMS. AMENITIES INCLUDE POOL WITH AREAS TO ENTERTAIN, TENNIS COURT, GYM, AND PLAYGROUND. 24/7 FRONT GATE GUARD AS WELL AS PATROLLING GUARD ON PREMISES.

BEAUTIFUL GARDEN CONDO WITH UPDATED KITCHEN AND BATHROOM. ITS A 2/2 WITH A FULLSIZE WASHER & DRYER INSIDE UNIT. FURNITURE IS OPTIONAL. GREAT COMMUNITY WITH POOL AND PLENTY OF AMENTITIES. 24 HR SECURITY AND GUARD GATE. PERFECT LOCATION CLOSE TO ALL.

Highly desirable 2/2 villa with two parking spaces directly in front of property. High vaulted ceilings, ceramic tiles throughout. A/C unit 3 years old, Stacked washer/dryer. Large fenced patio area. New roof and new exterior painting being completed by the association. This beauty will not last.

Rarely available, waterfront house with NO Association. Well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single family home in quite neighborhood. Enjoy direct lakefront views from the comfort of your Home. Patio has plenty of space to create your private oasis. Excellent location minutes away from schools, shopping, dining and major highways. Ready for your personal touches.  Lake allows for motorized boating! Act now, will not last. Perfect investment, ready to make it your own.

Only available unit @ Bonita Golf View. 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with private patio. 2 assigned parking spaces, washer and dryer in the unit. Low association fee includes water, exterior insurance and maintenance. Easy to show. It wont last.
Beautiful 2 bedroom 1 bathroom condo, totally renovated, tiled throughout - very centric ally located. This will sell fast!

Spacious & bright two story single family recently remodeled featuring: 3 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms 1 car garage with plenty of parking space. Tile throughout living area. The housing crisis is creating opportunities to design, innovate and be a part of Miamis development. Contact us immediately about this opportunity.

Attention investors!! Side by side duplex in area approved for multi-stories building. Located in desired location close to all amenities, major highways and Miami Health District. This is an income multifamily duplex in the area of up coming 16 Allapatha project. River landing shops and Marlins Park. Buy and make money with existing tenants or develop and make more Win/Win either way.

Distinct Pueblo style property on the West end of Little Havana within walking distance to Marlins Park. Four unit apartment building on a 7, 500 SF lot. Waste is included in the taxes, individual electric, new roofs on the structures, there is ample parking for each unit as well. Solid opportunity for someone interested in renovating or revitalization of a 1920s structure and add- value to this multifamily income property. Within 10 minutes of Brickell and Downtown. Miamis nationally recognized Little Havana neighborhood is known for its culturally-rich and colorful lifestyle. Great investment opportunity for those looking to take advantage of the overwhelming surge of growth and development in the area. Contact us now!

Eleventrust is proud to present its newest exclusive listing, Marlins Park 4- Plex - Little Havana.This newly constructed building consists of four (4) two bedroom/two bathroom apartments, featuring hurricane impact windows and doors, central a/c, private balcony, tile floors and modern kitchens and bathrooms equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The total rentable square footage is 3, 351 (average unit size is 837 sq. ft.). The individual units are being leased at $1, 600 a month in rent (or $1.91). Market rents in the area for this product type are at $1, 650 a month (or $1.97 sq. ft.). The projected Net Operating Income once fully occupied (Sept. 2020) is $52, 060 with a potential to grow to $54, 412 in year 2 with a 4.53% capitalization rate. No Parking.

Great opportunity for investors interested inMiami River district is in the process of redevelopment, with new restaurants, condominiums and mixed-use projects in the works. Great value.4 units close to major highways, hospitals, business center, all units have separate water and electricity services and are equipped with washer, dryer and assigned parking.

Mixed used corner development site currently in the permitting process. Site is in the heart of Allapattah, great accessibility to mayor freeways, 10 mins to Wynwood, Brickell and Downtown! 14 Residential units with 3 Commercial units. Will deliver shovel ready. 3 VACANT LOTS THAT ARE ZONED T4 - 18, 020 SF.

Great Opportunity and first time on the market in the fantastic neighborhood of Grapeland Heights! This is your chance to renovate and make this property your own or a great investment opportunity. Amazing starter home in a convenient location. Close to the Airport, Highways, the brand new River Landing Development, Downtown Miami, Coral Gables, and MUCH MORE. Property is being sold As-Is. Update 4/29 - ATTENTION: Highest and Best offer submission deadline is Tuesday, May 4, 2021, at Noon.
Ready to Sell !! Beauriful 2/2. unit. Modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Washer & Dryer in the unit. Building with great amenities.

This impeccable and spacious 2 bedrooms 2 baths apartment has plenty of closets space with a walk in closet in the master bedroom. Sunset Villas Phase III has a 24 hour security gate at entrance , swimming pool, play ground for the children, with a view to the lake. This community is located near Miami International Airport, Coral Gables, downtown Miami and 15 minutes to Miami Beach. This beautiful apartment can also be rented unfurnished for $1, 450.00 a month or furnished for $1, 750.00 a month on yearly leases only.

description: Currently producing $34, 200 in income/year, current tenants on a the 3/2 is on month-to-month and the 2/1.5 expires in May 2021. Property can produce up to 42, 000 a year with rents at current market prices. Property can produce as an AirBNB investment while you live in one unit and the other can produce up to 20k to 25k per year based on other property projections in the area. The home has remodel kitchens, hurricane shutters, both units have W/D, Original structure, no illegal additions, 12-year-old roof, all tiled. Each unit has a small backyard, all fenced. Parking for 6 cars, central a/c units, separate electricity and water meters. 7 minutes to coral gables/miracle mile and 5 minutes to Miami international Airport. Quiet neighborhood.

2021 Modern Construction of these 2 separated 2 story homes located in a fantastic central location. Each home is completely gated and features 3 bedrooms 3 1/2 bathrooms with 1 car garages. All porcelain tile flooring throughout. White shaker style kitchen cabinets with stainless steel appliances. Laundry/storage room. Modern floating cabinets in all the bathrooms with glass enclosed showers or tubs. High ceiling with plenty of natural sunlight! All hurricane impact windows and doors. Nice fenced backyards great for family BBQs. Walk in closets. Great for Airbnb! Close to the airport, Coral Gables, Downtown and Brickell. High end finishes throughout. Units can be sold separately for $700, 000. Easy to show. Bring your investors/clients and get it sold!

Two Folios 01-41-05-019-0120 ( 4, 868 sq ft Lot ) and 01-41-05-019-0121 ( 5, 634 sq ft Lot ). 2/1 and 2/1 and additional income producing lot. Call listing agent for more information. PLEASE DO NOT DISTURB TENANTS!
First floor: 1st unit (2 bds/1 ba) - 2nd unit (2bds/ 1ba), and 2nd floor: 1 unit(3 bds/1.5 ba) has separate meter. All units have their own AC unit.

STUNNING remodeled 3/3 single family home with all the upgrades. Minutes way from MIA, 836 and Coral Gables.Upgrades include beautifully remodeled bathrooms, kitchen with high-end appliances including wine cooler. Newer roof 2015, impact windows and doors. Huge master bedroom with large walking closet and view to the gorgeous back yard and pool. Great outdoor entertainment area with lush landscaping. Electrical fence for easy access to parking spaces. A must see bring your clients to see this immaculate home. Showings by appointment only please contact listing agent to schedule.

Excellent location. Home is in the heart of Miami. 2 bedroom, 1 remodeled bathroom, spacious living area, and an updated kitchen. It has an additional space on the porch for office use or a guestroom. Close to major highways, shopping and public transportation. Motivated Sellers.

Seller Motivated. 1/1 apartment can be used for owner occupancy or lease. Building has Impact Windows. Laundry Room in Building. Call Listing Agent for showing instructions. Tenant Occupied until end of April.

Attention Investors!!! 2 Bedroom 1 Bath condo centrally located. Remote controlled gated entry to parking, building key entry to lobby area. Unit is currently rented till Nov 30th, 2021 for $1, 350 per month. Monthly maintenance fee $243.34 includes insurance & water. Serious buyers only need inquire. Showings by appointment only and must provide proof of funds or pre-qual letter prior showings.

Great opportunity to own this income producing property in a desirable location. Main house is a 2 bed 2 bath plus bonus room. Tile through. Newly remodeled bathroom and kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Includes very large attached room used as a work space. Tons of potential. Detached in-law quarters with 2 bed 1 bath. Must see... Easy to show. Call or text listing agent for showing.

Finally! A Home that can adapt to todays changing needs near Coral Gables! This 4 bedroom 3 bath property can adapt to a big family, the in-laws, or even airbnb. You can be together or have your own separate entrance. This property has been well maintained. All cast iron pipes have been replaced with PVC, property has accordion shutters on all windows, stainless steal appliances, remodeled bathrooms, outdoor gazebo area, and fruit trees. Many possibilities being zoned duplex and on a corner lot. Plenty of green space to play or plant. This property will be shown for the first time on Sunday April 11th, 2021 between 1 and 4 pm. At the moment there arent any showings available during the week. I will accompany all showings so please do not approach the occupants without an appointment.

3 BR 2.5 BA Home in The Alhambra. Single family home, this Beauty features bathrooms with top of the line fixtures, kitchen features a stainless appliances including a wine cooler.Paved driveway, community pool....close to Doral, airport and major expressways. Schools Grade A. Low HOA.Tenants lease expires 12/14/21, they pay $ 2350 per month.

Summit Chase Condo is known to the local community as one of the most desirable places to live in the Fontainebleau area. Completely fenced in with a guard house at the entry of the property. Featuring 2 bedrooms 2 Full bathrooms, with Over sized bedrooms. Walk in closets, ample living room area. This will FLY. Community with 24 hours security guard, electronic gate entrance, secure parking lot. 1 assigned parking and plenty of visitor parking. The condominium offers Olympic Size Swimming Pool, Club House, Tennis Courts. Building just passed the 40 year recertification! AS LOW AS 3% DOWN PAYMENT. BUILDING HAS 10% RESERVES.

SPACIOUS ONE BEDROOM + DEN, LOCATED AT A VERY WELL MAINTAINED HOA. LISTING IS LOCATED IN A GATED COMMUNITY WITH POOL AND CLEAN ENVIRONMENT. GREAT LOCATION CLOSE TO 836 DOWTOWN , MIAMI INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, SHOPPING, WALKING DISTANCE TO RESTAURANTS, BANKS, COMMODITIES, ETC. UNIT COMES WITH PLENTY OF STORAGE SPACE. Tenants will move out prior to closing.No HOA assessments. Preferred showings during week days after 5:30pm or weekends with 24-advance notice.

Amazing corner 2 bedroom 2 bathroom with covered balcony, 2 parking spots, swimming pool in a clean and quiet building next to everything Miami has to offer. Beautiful master bathroom with Spanish tile, led, large walk . Water/Sewer included in condo fee, laundry on the same floor, plenty of light. Conveniently located close to SR-836, MIA and everything else Miami has to offer. 20 minutes to the beaches. This building does not budget reserves. Requires conventional financing with 25% down payment or 10% down payment with HELOC as secondary option. Shopping plaza and restaurants are all a short drive away. RENTAL PERMITTED AFTER A YEAR.
Great 2bed/1 bath unit on a centrally located building. Enjoy complex pool, tennis court and gym. Great investment property!!!

Great location in an established, centrally located neighborhood! Charming home, well kept and has original wood floors and tile. Large backyard with a small deck and fruit trees. This house has huge potential for anyone looking to make it their own and to their taste. Come and see it..it wont last! Call listing agent

This is a beautiful apartment located in the heart of Miami, close to everything. Updated kitchen and bathrooms, laundry inside the unit with new washer and dryer, spacious walk in closet, large patio ( larger model of the complex), updated pool, this is a must see! Association includes: water, trash removal, exterior insurance and maintenance of the common areas.
Great investment property. 2/1 and 1/1 in a very desirable area. Property will be completely vacant at time of closing. A must see.

Live in one of Miamis most desirable areas. This remodeled 2 Bedroom 2.5 Bath two story condo is gorgeous. Property has a nice size patio and feels like a Townhouse. Location is next expressway and many shops. Property is gated and is in a beautiful residential community. Unit has brand new white marble floors on the first floor and dark brown wood floors on second floor. This unit will not last. Low Association Fees!

Can Only be shown during the OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, MARCH 13 from 9AM to 2 PM. Great home in the heart of MIAMI! Opportunity to live with your in-laws or good for investor. Nice patio and perfect for entertaining and enjoying the Florida weather. Estate Sale. Subject to Probate Approval.

Great corner unit 2/2 apartment on the second floor. Nice updated bathrooms and kitchen. Lots of natural light. New A/C. accordion shutters. New Titan water heather. Washer and dryer inside the unit. HOA covers, common areas, water, trash, insurance, pool, gym, etc. Excellent location!! Great for investors or end users!! Come see it today and make it your own- Easy to show

Come back in this pristine remodeled home in the heart of Miami. Easy care ceramic flooring compliment this step saver floor plan. Modern kitchen with granite counters, stainless appliances and a well appointed bath. Super complex complete with pool, basketball, tennis, boat ramp, 1 parking space plus 1 guest parking. Well maintained complex and convenient to all Miami has to offer! Currently rented until June 1, 2021. Text or call listing agent to show, you wont be disappointed in this gem!

location, Location, Location! Just a few minutes from Miami International Airport! Rarely available. Amazing 3 bedroom 2 bath Corner unit, centrally located with views of Coral Gables and Downtown Miami. This unit has all the space you will need, plenty of closet space and includes a huge utility closet inside the unit. Tile throughout and IMPACT WINDOWS including the enclosed balcony. This unit has 2 assigned parking spaces for your convenience and plenty of visitor parking area. Great amenities in the building include a pool and jacuzzi. Laundry facilities are located on the same floor, water and sewer is also included in the maintenance and the 836 is just a few minutes away for easy access to all of Miami.

Great place to call home. Ideal for Owner Occupant or an Investor. This unit is remodeled with a new Kitchen and bathroom. New appliances. The Ac is less than 3 years old. Unit features large bedrooms. Large closets. Corner unit has windows in all the bedrooms. Nice views from the rooms. Centrally located building minutes to Miami Downtown, Coral Gables, and the Beaches. Easy access to major roadways and public transportation. Only 45 units in the building so the pool is never crowded. Also gated parking for one car and lots of street parking. easy to show. The association has NO RESERVES.

description: 2 Beds + Den / 3 Full Bathrooms. Come and Enjoy the luxury Living! Building nominated as the Most Amenities in the World including Basketball Court, 5 pools, Spa, Gym with boxing area, Bbq Kitchen, Virtual Golf, Recording Studio, Racquetball, Yoga, Sunrise pool, & Kids play Area. Soon the Soccer field, Sky-deck, Observatory to view stars with telescopes, Tennis courts, Jacuzzi in the 58rd floor overlooking the whole city and more will be finished. Unit includes 1 car-parking and 1 valet included with rent. Cable, Internet, Water, Trash and Sewer Included in Rent. Just Steps from Metro Mover, Virgin Train Station, Bayside, Port of Miami, American Airlines Arena, Museums, Adrienne Arsht Center and more.

A truly rare opportunity to own a one-of-a-kind completely remodeled and already combined double residence with 6Bed/6Bath currently configured as 4-bedrooms, 5-bathrooms, plus a movie theater/media room, plus an office/library. This spectacular mansion in the sky covers the entire eastern front of the building with 180-degree direct water views of the bay and Ocean. This incredible residence offers nearly 6, 000 total sf in one of the newest luxury high-rises in the Heart of Miami. Double private elevators take you to two private foyers, where you will discover double glass doors opening up to your Miami mansion with the best views in all of Miami. This spacious home is ready for you to create your own paradise in the Arts & Entertainment District.

FOR INVESTORS ONLY! UNIT IS RENTED UNTIL MARCH 4th 2022. $2000 a month. Cozy studio in brand new development Paramount Miami World Center. Only guest suite unit which includes at no extra cost, 1 parking space assigned (self parking), 1 valet parking and 1 storage space assigned. Features include white tile floors, 10 ft high ceilings, upgraded kitchen with top of the line Bosch appliances, full washer and dryer, built in closet, shade blinds, spacious bathroom, floor to ceiling Windows, high end finishes and more. A lifestyle and entertainment for daily enjoy. A building you never have to leave. Have access to more tan 45 amenities including 5 pools, conservatory, jam room, recording studio, basketball court, racquetball court, state of the art fitness center, boxing, yoga room, spa, etc.

A truly rare opportunity to own 2 side-by-side 3Bed/4Bath+Den residences easily convertible into a 6Bed/8Bath residence, covering the entire eastern front of the building with 180-degree direct water views of the bay and Ocean.
